						               													<description>From the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ALL ABOARD! The Long, Long Locomotive is leaving the station and it's full steam ahead for matching fun!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This Flip-A-Longs game is a high-speed adventure where players must have a keen sense of memory as they match scenes to create the longest train on the tracks. Higher level critical thinking is required, imagination is encouraged, and vocabularies are enhanced&amp;#10;in play with Flip-A-Long cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Flip-A-Longs cleverly combines puzzle play and memory matching to create an engaging new game that children and adults alike will &amp;quot;FLIP&amp;quot; for! Simply flip over cards, if you find a match, add it to your train to make yours the longest!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Who will be riding on your train? A marching band? A roller  coaster? Spooky ghosts? The player to match the most card and build the longest train wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Dynamic game play and silly illustrations encourage memory, matching, counting, dexterity and more! Flip-A-Longs is a game the entire family can play!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
